'''{{PAGENAME}}''' ke nngwe ya diporofinsi mo [[Aferika Borwa]].(leina la kgaolo e le ne la fetloga go tsweng kwa go '''Eastern Transvaal''' ka kgwedi ya Phatwe a tlhola masome a mabedi le bone ka ngwaga wa 1995), ke kgaolo e e mo Aferika Borwa . Leina la lefelo le lone ka boripana le raya "kwa letsatsi le tlhabang teng" ka teme ya Seswazi, Sexhosa, Setebele gape le Sezulu. Mpumalanga o ikaegile kwa botlhaba jwa Afrika Borwa , mo bokone jwa KwaZulu-Natal gape o boe o aga molelwane le lefatsheng la Swaziland le Mozambique. E akaretsa selekanyo sa 6.5% sa lefatshe la Aferika Borwa. Mo bokone e aga molelwane kwa Limpopo, mme mo bophiri ke Gauteng, mme mo bokone bophirima ke Free Statemme gape kwa bokone ke KwaZulu-Natal.Toropokgolo ya teng e bidiwa [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nelspruit Nelspruit] (mme gompieno e fetlotswe leina go nna Mbombela).Mme ka ngwaga wa 1994, Mpumalanga e kile ya bo e le bontlha bongwe jwa kgaolo ya [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transvaal_Province Transvaal_Province].

==Popego ya lefatshe==
Drakensberg ke ene yo o kgaoganyang  Mpumalanga ka matlhakore a le mabedi ebong bontlha jo bongwe jwa bophirima jo bo tetseng bojang jo bontsi bo ikadile ka mo go kgatlhisang gape lefatshe le bo le tsholetsegela fa godimo mme gape mo letlhakoreng la botlhaba go fologela tlase bojang mme bo se bontsi mo kalo mme teng fa go nale diphologolo tse di mefutla tse di anameng le tikologo gape di e kgabisa. Bontlha jwa borwa jwa lefelo la diphologolo la [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kruger_National_Park Kruger_National_Park] bo bonwa teng mo kgaolong. Thaba ya Drakensberg e fetla boleele jwa selekanyo sa  2000m mo mafelong a le mantsi bogoljang mo bogare jwa kgaolo ya Mpumalanga e e leng yone e tlwaelesegile ka ditlhaba tse dintsi<ref>http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drakensberg</ref>. 

==Bojanala==
Mpumalanga gape o tumile ka go itsege e le lefelo la bojanala. [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kruger_National_Park Kruger_National_Park], ke lefelo le sireletsang diphologolo le le simolodisitsweng ka ngwaga wa 1898 maikaelelo e le go sireletsa le gone go tlhokomela diphologolo tsa naga, lefelo le le botona jwa selekanyo sa dokhilomethara di le 20,000 square (7,700 sq mi), mme ebile le itsege lefatshe ka bophara[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kruger_National_Park Kruger_National_Park]<ref>http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kruger_National_Park</ref>.

==Dipuo le dipalo tsa batho==
Palo ya batho e ka tshwara 30% ba bua [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SiSwati SiSwati], teme ya batho ba lefatshe la Swaziland ka gore ba bapile fela thata, ba le  26% bone ba bua puo ya [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IsiZulu IsiZulu], 10.3% [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IsiNdebele IsiNdebele], 10,2% [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northern_Sotho Northern_Sotho]sa kwa bokone le 11,6% yone e bua [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Xitsonga Xitsonga].

